# Evocable PWA - Next.js 15 Audiobook App

## Architecture
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 App Router + TypeScript
- **UI**: React 19 + Tailwind CSS + Lucide icons
- **State**: TanStack Query (server) + Zustand (client)
- **Storage**: IndexedDB (Dexie) + PWA offline support
- **Forms**: react-hook-form + Zod validation

## Key Directories
- [src/app/](mdc:src/app/) - Next.js App Router (pages/layouts)
- [src/components/](mdc:src/components/) - Components organized by:
  - `features/` - Feature-specific (auth, library, upload, player)
  - `ui/` - Reusable UI components
  - `common/` - Shared layout components
- [src/lib/](mdc:src/lib/) - Utilities, API client, auth
- [src/hooks/](mdc:src/hooks/) - Custom React hooks
- [src/types/](mdc:src/types/) - TypeScript definitions

## Supported Formats
PDF, EPUB, TXT → Audiobook conversion

## Core Dependencies
`@tanstack/react-query` `zustand` `dexie` `react-hook-form` `zod` `class-variance-authority` `tailwind-merge` `next-pwa`

